00:00:21.900 --> 00:00:26.230
In this episode, we’ll talk about the pantheon
of deities in Indian myths.

00:00:26.230 --> 00:00:30.419
Unlike myths from Egypt and the Ancient Near
East, there are living people for whom these

00:00:30.419 --> 00:00:33.469
stories have deep, personal, religious meaning.

00:00:33.469 --> 00:00:37.730
Remember how it got a little uncomfortable
